data.description: Welcome to this stunning residence nestled on an oversized lot in Fort Thomas. This remarkable home exudes charm and character with its exquisite stained-glass windows and gleaming hardwood floors throughout. As you enter, you're greeted by a spacious living area, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family. The second level boasts three generously sized bedrooms, with dual cooling on each floor Additionally, a versatile fourth bedroom flex room offers endless possibilities for use, whether as a home office, playroom, or guest quarters. Downstairs, the finished basement provides even more living space with a cozy family room and an additional full bath, ideal for accommodating guests or creating a private retreat. Outside, the property features a driveway porch, deck and patio perfect for enjoying your morning coffee with spectacular views of downtown Cincinatti with its manicured landscaping and curb appealDon't miss your chance to own this absolutely stunning home in  Fort Thomas in highland school district
